  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 91,
   "id": "756c4c77",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "out=['CreditScore','Age','NumOfProducts']\n",
    "for i in out:\n",
    "    for x in [i]:\n",
    "        q75,q25 = np.percentile(df.loc[:,x],[75,25])\n",
    "        intr_qr = q75-q25\n",
    "\n",
    "        max = q75+(1.5*intr_qr)\n",
    "        min = q25-(1.5*intr_qr)\n",
    "\n",
    "        df.loc[df[x] < min,x] = df[i].mode()\n",
    "        df.loc[df[x] > max,x] = df[i].mode()"
   ]
  },
